Title: Operator approach to the Gluing Theorem in String Field Theory

Authors: Abdulmajeed Abdurrahman (Rutherford Lab.), Jose Bordes and Cristobal

Lara (Univ. de Valencia)Comments: 11 LaTex pages

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A33 (2000) 4851-4858

An algebraic proof of the Gluing Theorem at tree level of perturbation theoryin String Field Theory is given. Some applications of the theorem to closedstring non-polynomial action are briefly discussed